headline: Realtor.com速 Survey Finds 81% of Potential Sellers Think They Will Get Their Asking Price or More This Year
summary: Sellers across the U.S. are optimistic heading into this year's Best Time to Sell with 70% of potential sellers thinking it is a good time to sell, according to a new survey from Realtor.com速 out today. Although market conditions are not a driver of the decision, today's sellers are optimistic about selling this year because of their ability to take advantage of the increased value of homes and an expectation that buyer-offers will meet their asking price.
